name: J.Long
description: '''Jaime Lynn Long''' (born June 10, 1985), better known by his stage name '''J.Long''', is an American Christian singer, songwriter & multi instrumentalist. He was a frequent collaborator with [[hip hop]] group [[Pretty Ricky]], and also featured the group on his own song "Personal Freak". In April 2015, before departing from the music industry, Long toured one last time with his bandmates in Europe. He remained on hiatus until releasing new music in 2023.
